</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Ortlyeb, als ir uns vormals
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von eins übelteters
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, den ir in
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> fenknuss habt, also hat uns unser
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> graf <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        von <expan>Öting<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> zu
                        Amberg, seid <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er ewch hab geheissen
                        gehabt, <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> übelteter <expan>zu
                            v<ex>er</ex>suchen</expan>. Der hab bekant, daz er Friczen von
                                <expan>Kam<ex>m</ex></expan>, <expan>crom<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, das sein <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        hab; ob <add>der</add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dem <expan>nachkome<ex>n</ex></expan> wölte so
                        möcht er hinausz <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so sölt im
                                <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> recht geen und
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>farn</expan>. Nu was der
                            <expan>crom<ex>er</ex></expan> auf <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit
                        bey uns niht anheim, daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Ötinge<ex>n</ex></expan> niht wol
                                <expan>treffenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darczu
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> konden. Derselb Fricz von
                                <expan>Kam<ex>m</ex></expan> ist <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> seid
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heim</expan>
<expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> und wil <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                        ewch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch mit fleiss, ir wellet im umb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hilfflich und
                            <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> darinn sein. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Margar<ex>ete</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
